             was indicted for <rs id="t17960217-30-off175" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17960217-30-off175" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960217-30-off175" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17960217-30-cd176" type="crimeDate">31st of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17960217-30-off175 t17960217-30-cd176"></join>, one thousand seven hundred and twenty-eight iron screws; value 15s. eighteen thousand nails, value 1l. and three thousand other nails, value 35s. the property of 
                     <persName id="t17960217-30-victim328" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Knight
