                  , in their dwelling-house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17960217-30-person331">
                  RICHARD
                   KNIGHT
               <interp inst="t17960217-30-person331" type="surname" value="KNIGHT"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17960217-30-person331" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>
